{"tid":2508803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"五一懲罰祭 號召購物師（李八方）","createTime":"2021-04-29T04:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T07:10:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1b772ad481560c1f4b7c04fe683faddab4f33da7","tid":2508803,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/MOHKWVJ4BVAE5HCOB5IQTINX7M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FMOHKWVJ4BVAE5HCOB5IQTINX7M%2F&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=f6e3d2bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FMOHKWVJ4BVAE5HCOB5IQTINX7M%2F&h=25e65a9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/MOHKWVJ4BVAE5HCOB5IQTINX7M/</a><br />\n<br />\n五一懲罰祭 號召購物師（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Z1wAPACu463T4pXbiGwyZ8uig2I=/510x303/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BXWG7UE4OZCANDQ4N654SMPBAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZ1wAPACu463T4pXbiGwyZ8uig2I%3D%2F510x303%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBXWG7UE4OZCANDQ4N654SMPBAU.jpg&h=8c941864&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無能嘅政府抗疫成績有目共睹，搞到香港民不聊生，唔少小商戶都因為咁吊晒鹽水甚至頂唔順執笠。呢個時候香港人想繼續撐落去，相信又係要靠自救啦，嚟緊五一「黃金周」，黃色經濟圈就有人吹響集結號，呼籲大家再展開懲罰行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「懲罰Mee」App即將上架<br />\n<br />\n「Mee懲罰師」呢星期喺facebook專頁公告，招募「五一懲罰祭」嘅參與商戶，行動觸發點之一係月初海關打壓阿布泰，引發足足成個星期嘅懲罰風潮。當時唔只香港人連續多日排隊爆買，仲有多間黃店以行動聲援阿布泰，實行重現「一方有難，八方支援」嘅港人精神！<br />\n<br />\n不過，急需大家集體懲罰嘅商店點只一間，今年尚未過半，社會氣氛極低迷，疫情反覆之餘政府又屢借抗疫為名打壓小店，搞到好多店舖都掙扎求存，餐廳受「安心出行」影響固然係重災區，零售市道亦都一蹶不振，仲有行業因為抗疫政策至今未能復業，所以「Mee懲罰師」團隊繼上年後再搞懲罰祭，喺5月1至9日舉行黃金周活動，橫跨兩個周末，希望透過同路人集體懲罰兼夾母親節效應，為黃店帶嚟更多營業額，為一眾黃店商戶提供喘息機會，同時亦為黃色經濟圈注入新動力，另外仲會有個「懲罰Mee」App將喺5.1上架，畀大家單撈。<br />\n<br />\n有黃店就言話上年參加過懲罰祭，幫到生意好多，仲多咗人識佢哋；亦有黃店直截了當留言話「名已報」，反應非常唔錯，咁政權唔畀大家上街，大家咪改為行街囉！<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"5556f1653e91ee69777d529baf286efdd332cca6","tid":2508803,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:06:23.000Z","msg":"要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae4a135218f96a52b0b3170c25338dccb7b99eb","tid":2508803,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6de2c396c28473a70f33766521994b7f3c7cbfb","tid":2508803,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:11:43.000Z","msg":"心諗李八方係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來係筆名"},{"pid":"ceeed303668f6f20613a55e28c34f9e6b113a14f","tid":2508803,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6de2c396c28473a70f33766521994b7f3c7cbfb","tid":2508803,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:11:43.000Z","msg":"心諗李八方係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來係筆名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:48:58.000Z","msg":"十多年前，沒什麼網媒、沒有立場新聞，這樣做新聞很大逆不道。沒有這位小編輯努力陪我上刀山玩大鑊，還有社長董橋的開明，相關好同事自願或被迫同我哋癲，根本不可能有那時候令江湖起浪、政商界像被鬼責的<span class=\"orange\">李八方</span>。很明顯他才是我老細，每天我請准他才敢放工，他會說：「我用完你個腦喇，走啦。」在下才告退。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210424/VV6A5SN3DRG4JIHCWMKUP2NPLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210424%2FVV6A5SN3DRG4JIHCWMKUP2NPLM%2F&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=833d65c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210424%2FVV6A5SN3DRG4JIHCWMKUP2NPLM%2F&h=6acf5085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210424/VV6A5SN3DRG4JIHCWMKUP2NPLM/</a>"},{"pid":"124d6498ad456c26baa065b1f69c4758a75750e1","tid":2508803,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7c0452bd92dffa4c20d4ec93bcfcdfac85c013","tid":2508803,"uid":159271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:53:10.000Z","msg":"推。等download"},{"pid":"b3aac8187d6fe8fa0c2a8f320fb64fe7e27dbfa5","tid":2508803,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeaFLtdmES3tGjWAj95A5t7tSgy7G9SK9xfBYXWuw9sgG?filename=Mwts2Xm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMwts2Xm.jpg&h=ca94c3d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"734e9c9fa5aa8f8103c3b32e5ce5bc58969b3c8b","tid":2508803,"uid":56248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:10:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}